data.description: Excellent...''One Owner''...Fully Renovated...2044 Square Foot Palm Harbor double wide on TIE DOWN FOUNDATION with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 car garage on 10 Fully Fenced ACRES with Incredible VIEWS of Mingus, Thumb Butte, Granite Mountain, & the Bradshaw's...This fine home has all NEW Paint inside & out, GREAT ROOM Concept, NEW Wood Plank Luxury Vinyl, Vaulted Ceilings, Wood Burning Stove, NEW Horizontal Blinds, NEW Outlets/Covers, Sky Lights, & Ceiling Fans. Kitchen is well appointed with Oak Cabinets, NEW Laminate Countertops, Farm/Apron Sink, Stainless Steel Appliances, & Walk-In Pantry. Master is Spacious, has Large Walk-In Closet, Tub/Shower Combo, & Single Sink. Additional features include, Huge Covered Rear Patio, Laundry Room, NEW Well, NEW Roof, New HVAC, NEW 50 Gallon Water Heater, 24'x36' Pole Barn, & is in Turnkey Condition!!!
